        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Literature value. The worldwide production of polydimethlsiloxane was somewhat above 2 million metric tonnes in 2002, corresponding to a market value of 8000 million EUR (European Commission, 2007). Reference(s): European Commission. 2007. Integrated Pollution Prevention and Control, Reference Document on Best Available Techniques for the Production of Speciality Inorganic Chemicals. Retreived online from: http://eippcb.jrc.ec.europa.eu/reference/, 18 July 2017.</productionVolumeComment>
